want to do now?

1334
01:31:54,370 --> 01:31:59,105
<i>The way I see it,
we can do whatever we want.</i>

1335
01:34:25,640 --> 01:34:27,569
I need you
to stay quiet.

1336
01:34:27,570 --> 01:34:30,539
This is a "me" thing.
