1337
01:34:30,540 --> 01:34:34,275
- You got that?
- <i>Fine, but make it quick.</i>

1338
01:34:38,010 --> 01:34:39,569
Open on five.

1339
01:34:39,570 --> 01:34:43,305
Go. Opening up.

